column5: No no no .... not what you were thinking ....  Wee Wee Chew aMerry Chreesmas  Was just wondering how long its been since I was last out carolling (probably more than 15 years ago - when the kids were young) ... how bout you ?
Yeah, I did some Carols.  Marys and Suzies and Floozies too, but the singing wasn't Christmas related.
